<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #ffc107; color: #000; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .game-details { background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .game-details strong { display: inline-block; width: 120px; }
        .old-date { text-decoration: line-through; color: #dc3545; }
        .new-date { color: #28a745; font-weight: bold; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #ffc107; color: #000; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>⚠️ Zmiana Terminu Meczu</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Cześć {{ player.fullName }}!</p>

        <p>Informujemy o zmianie terminu meczu w <strong>{{ game.league.name }}</strong>.</p>

        <div class="game-details">
            <p><strong>Stary termin:</strong> <span class="old-date">{{ oldDate|date('d.m.Y H:i') }}</span></p>
            <p><strong>Nowy termin:</strong> <span class="new-date">{{ game.gameDate|date('d.m.Y H:i') }}</span></p>
            <p><strong>Liga:</strong> {{ game.league.name }}</p>

            {% if game.isTeamGame %}
                <p><strong>{{ game.teamA.name }}</strong> vs <strong>{{ game.teamB.name }}</strong></p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <p>Prosimy o zaktualizowanie swojego kalendarza!</p>

        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{ url('admin') }}?crudAction=detail&crudControllerFqcn=App\\Controller\\Admin\\GameCrudController&entityId={{ game.id }}" class="button">
                Zobacz szczegóły meczu
            </a>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Nyska Liga Bowlingowa<br>
            To jest automatyczna wiadomość, nie odpowiadaj na nią.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
